import React from "react";

const File = () => {
  return (
    <svg
      width="24px"
      height="24px"
      viewBox="0 0 24 24"
      fill="none"
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    >
      <path
        d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8l-6-6Z"
        stroke="currentColor"
        strokeLinecap="round"
        stroklinejoin="round"
      ></path>
      <path
        d="M14 2v6h6M16 17H8"
        stroke="currentColor"
        strokeLinecap="round"
        strokeLinejoin="round"
      ></path>
      <path d="M20 12H4" stroke="currentColor"></path>
    </svg>
  );
};

export default File;
